Changelog — Soryn’s Lobby Manager v3.2.3

✨ New Features

• Username Input on Login

Users can input desired username on login

• Welcome Screen with License Duration

Informative welcome so users know their license duration

• User Interface Improvements

Better visual aesthetics

• Right-Click Changelog Access

Users can right click anywhere to view recent changes

• Auto Update Download Location 📥

Auto updates now let you select where to download to (this update still defaults to Downloads folder, but next update will reflect your choice)

• Bots Deploy Field Upgrades 🤖⚡

Bots can now deploy field upgrades during matches

🛠️ Fixes

• Fixed a bug where closing a tab while fullscreened would make other buttons disappear or become unclickable
